track_notes: You have to walk 15km for this summit. Park at the village Argens, plenty room on summit.

Do not try this track if you are not used of mode Goat; as i have a 4 wheel drive i could drive on a forest road and start at 1480m i could have go up to 1703m, i did not. the first part of ascent is very easy on a forest road, but the end is very hard in between rocks, and the slope is quite hard! do not descend the way i used unless you are a GOAT. there is few other way to reach this summit.
